name: Udo_Lin_Xoir
content:
Udo Lin Xoir was a lead analyst of an unknown species from Iokath who worked with master designer Vel Jyc Boer, someone who Udo Lin Xoir greatly admired. Udo Lin Xoir worked on Test environment WL428T73.
Udo Lin Xoir is mentioned in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Eternal Throne in the codex entry 'History of Iokath: Entry 3'.
